data.description: Fixer Alert!  Greyhaven Condo with great floor plan needs TLC, but will be a great investment!  Must be a cash sale due to condition. Well maintained complex has easy access to bus lines and shopping.  Needs paint-flooring & wall work in kitchen.  Units have a fenced and gated front area as well as a small back yard that is fenced. 2 large BR and bath and a guest bath downstairs.  There is a fireplace and slider to the back yard. Most windows are triple pane.  See extended remarks for more info. Water leak from bath upstairs caused damage to kitchen ceiling.  Repair to pipe is done - Cosmetic work to fix sheetrock needs to be done, and cabinets re-hung.  Needs new kitchen stove.  This is a Probate Sale and is subject to court approval and possible overbid at the hearing.  BUYER BAILED AT THE LAST MINUTE--TAKE A LOOK!  GREAT POTENTIAL FOR FLIPPER, INVESTOR OR FIRST TIME HOME BUYER.  CLA for details.
